<NEW>

The PROTOHUMANS have left the area, a few pieces of scattered fruit
and a couple of baskets are the only thing left marking their
presence.

The only thing left now is the silent statue, the one looking just
like the Predacon BLIGHT. It stands about 20 feet tall, which is
almost three times as tall as the Predacon himself is. A few baskets
of fruit still lay at its feet.

All of this is sitting in a rather large clearing surrounded by trees
and bushes. The question is what will the MAXIMALS do? Will they
examine the statue? Follow the PROTOHUMANS? Go back to the ARK? Or do
they have something else in mind?

(TAG)
